ElSereno — AUTHORS
==================

This file lists the individuals who have contributed to the
design, implementation, and documentation of ElSereno.

Primary author + maintainer
---------------------------

Daniel Solís Agea <daniel.solis@zynap.com>
    LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/danisolis/
