              every signed release tag (v1.0.0, v1.0.1, v1.1.0)

Acknowledgements
----------------

- The Go, pgx, goreleaser, cosign, SLSA, and Sigstore projects
  whose reusable supply-chain infrastructure makes this release
  pipeline auditable end-to-end.
- The OPC Foundation, IEC TC 57, IEEE Power and Energy Society
  (1815 DNP3 WG), HART Communication Foundation, ASHRAE SSPC
  135 (BACnet), Modicon / Schneider, and Rockwell / ODVA for
  the public protocol specifications that make write-gate
  enforcement decidable at the wire layer.

Contact for security issues
---------------------------

Please email daniel.solis@zynap.com with subject line prefix
`[ElSereno Security]`. See SECURITY.md for the full vulnerability
disclosure policy.
